tc.compiler.tree.visit

Interface TreeVisitor<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Analyze, Dump, Encode, PreprocessClassDeclarations, TreeVisitorBase

    public interface TreeVisitor<T>
    All visitor classes for ASTs will implement this interface, which is parameterized by return type.
